Summary: These faces flowing down from the sky showed up in my photo, didn't see them with my eyes.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was out taking sunset shots and then I felt like I should take a shot of the eastern sky (opposite side from sunset). When I looked at the photo I noticed these facelike shapes flowing down from the sky. I was amazed at what I was seeing!! I did not hear anything or see anything unusual when I took the picture, just a plain sky shot and not one I would normally be inspired to photograph. I was simply"told" to shoot here so I did. now I know why. The first shot is the original,second one is enlarged and enhanced to define the faces.
